ance-asceticism-zuhd"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-91z","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":27322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/01\/ibn-abbas-respond-firawn\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Greeting: I would respond to Pharaoh if he greeted me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf Pharaoh had said to me, \u2018May Allah bless you,\u2019 I would have said, \u2018And you too,\u2019 but Pharaoh has already died.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 1098 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6358,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/13\/beware-minor-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sin: Beware of committing many minor sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cO Aisha, beware of seemingly insignificant bad deeds. Verily, they have a pursuer from Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4243 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/ibn-umar-pithy-advice\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Ibn Umar asks the Prophet for pithy advice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, give me a word and make it short that I might understand it.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not be angry.\u201d I repeated my question twice and each time the Prophet responded, \u201cDo not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19538,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/20\/dua-love-strength\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: O Allah, grant me your love, strengthen me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Yazid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would supplicate, saying, \u201cO Allah, grant me your love and the love of those whose love will benefit me with you. O Allah, whatever you have provided me from what I love, make it strength for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37263,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/27\/ask-for-maqam-mahmud\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wasilah: Ask Allah to bring the Prophet near to Him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk Allah to grant me the means of approach. Verily, a servant does not ask for it in the world but that I will be a witness for him or intercede for him on the Day\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34269,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/17\/dua-between-two-sujood\/","url_meta":{"origin":34693,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Supplication between the two prostrations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 17, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, used to say between the two prostrations, \u201cO Allah, forgive me, have mercy on me, restore me, guide me, and provide for me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 284 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0